                  <desc type="MagicFormula">A magic formula to hinder a captive from escaping has been added later at the top of the volume.</desc> 
                  <q xml:lang="gez">ከልሹት፡ ከልሹት፡ ምርያን፡ ቆሮተንደከኤል፡ በዝንቱ፡ አስማቲከ፡ ዘአሰ<supplied resp="PRS10747Zotenbe">ደ</supplied>ከ፡
                    ለብርያል <gap reason="omitted" extent="unknown"  resp="PRS10747Zotenbe"/></q>
                </item>
                
                <item xml:id="a2">
